{"tid":2281481,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[買電視] 有冇電視機選台唔使先揀analog digital","createTime":"2020-11-11T08:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T17:43:47.000Z","uid":362239,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfedf7452a234aba1a0c09751e8d0182f66d060","tid":2281481,"uid":362239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"請教下，有冇電視可以set到只需按冧巴，就自己識轉去analog或digital ？即係譬如：<br />\n<br />\n01 &gt;&gt; analog channel A<br />\n02 &gt;&gt; analog channel B<br />\n31 &gt;&gt; digital RTHK<br />\n99 &gt;&gt; digital ViuTV<br />\n<br />\n我見大部份電視，都要先按個制啪去analog定digital，然後再按台號，或者按個menu出嚟再用上下制選台，但我想搵部只按冧巴就知個台係analog定digital<br />\n<br />\n因為大廈閉路電視同衛星台仲係analog，所以冇得放棄analog<br />\n<br />\n如果係有得放落個「我的最愛」然後個我的最愛係用冧巴選台我都接受到"},{"pid":"f9285839a5b3a877563d5f37654e49da56dbdcbf","tid":2281481,"uid":36716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"我係無睇過任何評價就買左電視既人<br />\nTu8000 samsung <br />\n無分analog digital,不過佢無numpad, 得上下禁"},{"pid":"8efeff182ea2478047fa422aba0c0f667317cc60","tid":2281481,"uid":248518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:52:38.000Z","msg":"屋企用緊部Samsung印象中係mix嘅"},{"pid":"8dcfe7cb20208b59c72272e0a174c2522633a950","tid":2281481,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8efeff182ea2478047fa422aba0c0f667317cc60","tid":2281481,"uid":248518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:52:38.000Z","msg":"屋企用緊部Samsung印象中係mix嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\nSamsung識自己跳"},{"pid":"d7ccd1f655157f6d4296f4bf76ea74d608324913","tid":2281481,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"6年前買部LG係"},{"pid":"5e7009100a8afafb02f69eb47525f7f6a1a670b5","tid":2281481,"uid":362239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7ccd1f655157f6d4296f4bf76ea74d608324913","tid":2281481,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,